<span class="pubdate size11 darkgray" title="2003-11-12 10:45:00Z">Nov 12, 2003</span>
                
                

            </div>
			<span class="anthracite size13" contentbodystyle="Anthracite">In response to Pete and Brian, I think the "Drive By Spammer" part is definitely the relevant clue.  However, I can't see anybody who is semi-intelligent/knowledgable sitting around in a car even in a semi-remote vicinity.  I can see them doing it once or twice, to get everything setup, but after that I wouldn't dare be anywhere in the neighborhood.  But then again, if they are more of a script kiddie and they don't fully comprehend what it means, then that may very well be the case.  If the spammer is fairly competent, I would still have to vote that the two systems were being used against each other.</span>
		</div>
           
    <div class="spacer"></div>

    <div class="rule-gray"></div>
    <div class="spacer-small"></div>

    
